c: 28
v: 25
t: "Mulala khubeshikhana babili balia namwitsila nachenda nalola tsisoni, naboola mbu; “ papa akhulanganga mbu akhurunge omurungo kwokhunywesiliye.” Mana shingala 28. yamuulila mana namukanila omakhuwa kaye, yaboola mbu: “olaria tawe omalile okhuhonokokha okhurulana nende Abandu ababii.”"